Currently, JIRA Service Desk users cannot search the knowledge base that is linked to the Customer Portal.

In addition to the search bar (top-right of the page) not being available to these users, any attempt to use one of the search macros in a page results in the attached message.

It would be great to have the option to enable searching for Service Desk users, limited to the space(s) that they can view.

